                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-179-18561215 t18561215-179-punishment-80"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
